# Satu Payment Mode Switch - Documentation

## One Secret Controls Everything

| Secret Name | Values | What it does |
|-------------|--------|--------------|
| `PAYMENT_MODE` | `fake` or `live` | Switches between Fake Omise and Real Omise |

## How to Switch

### To Fake Mode (Testing - No Real Money)

```bash
npx wrangler secret put PAYMENT_MODE
# Enter: fake
```

Or via Cloudflare Dashboard:
1. Workers & Pages → `satu-api` → Settings → Variables
2. Edit `PAYMENT_MODE` secret
3. Change value to `fake`
4. Save

### To Live Mode (Production - Real Money)

```bash
npx wrangler secret put PAYMENT_MODE
# Enter: live
```

Also need `OMISE_SECRET_KEY` secret added (only for live mode).

## What Changes

| Mode | Payment URL | QR Code Source | Money Moves |
|------|-------------|----------------|-------------|
| `fake` | `fake-omise.csmittee.workers.dev` | Fake QR server | ❌ No |
| `live` | `api.omise.co` | Real Omise PromptPay | ✅ Yes |

## Verification

Check current mode:

```bash
curl https://api.janishammer.com/health
```

Response shows: `{"status":"ok","payment_mode":"fake",...}`

## Files That Use This Secret

| File | What it does |
|------|--------------|
| `src/handlers/order.js` | Reads `env.PAYMENT_MODE` to decide which payment gateway to call |
| `src/index.js` | Exposes `payment_mode` in `/health` endpoint for verification |

## No Code Change Needed

Change the secret. The Worker reads it instantly. No redeploy required.
